But clearly it can't
be too far different

00:32:47.860 --> 00:32:49.530
from special relativity
or we wouldn't

00:32:49.530 --> 00:32:51.447
have been able to formulate
special relativity

00:32:51.447 --> 00:32:52.250
in the first place.

